<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Intervention terminée</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #EDEAE4; font-family: 'DM Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"
  >
    <table
      role="presentation"
      width="100%"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      style="background-color: #EDEAE4; padding: 48px 20px;"
    >
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table
            role="presentation"
            width="580"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            style="max-width: 580px; width: 100%;"
          >
            <!-- Brand Header -->
            <tr>
              <td style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 36px;">
                <span style="font-size: 22px; color: #1C1917; letter-spacing: -0.5px;"
                  >{{ brandName }}</span
                >
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Main Card -->
            <tr>
              <td
                style="background-color: #FDFCFB; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #E8E3DC;"
              >
                <!-- Top accent line -->
                <div
                  style="height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1C1917 0%, #44403C 50%, #A8A29E 100%);"
                ></div>

                <!-- Header -->
                <div style="padding: 40px 56px 36px; border-bottom: 1px solid #F0EDE8;">
                  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="vertical-align: middle; width: 52px;">
                        <div
                          style="width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: #DCFCE7; border: 1.5px solid #BBF7D0; text-align: center; line-height: 44px; font-size: 18px;"
                        >
                          ✓
                        </div>
                      </td>
                      <td style="vertical-align: middle; padding-left: 16px;">
                        <p
                          style="margin: 0 0 2px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #6B7280;"
                        >
                          Mise à jour ticket
                        </p>
                        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 26px; color: #1C1917; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">
                          Intervention terminée
                        </p>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </div>

                <!-- Body -->
                <div style="padding: 36px 56px 40px;">
                  <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #44403C; font-weight: 300;">
                    Bonjour <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917;">{{ assigneeName }}</span>,
                  </p>

                  <p style="margin: 0 0 26px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; color: #57534E; font-weight: 300;">
                    Le prestataire <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917;">{{ providerName }}</span> a indiqué que l’intervention est
                    <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #16A34A;">terminée</span> sur le ticket ci-dessous.
                    Vous pouvez maintenant vérifier le résultat et clôturer le ticket si tout est conforme.
                  </p>

                  <!-- Ticket Info Block -->
                  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom: 28px;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="background-color: #F8F7F5; border: 1px solid #E8E3DC; border-radius: 4px; padding: 24px 28px;">
                        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
                          <tr>
                            <td style="width: 50%;">
                              <p style="margin: 0 0 3px; font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9CA3AF;">Référence</p>
                              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917;">{{ ticketId }}</p>
                            </td>
                            <td style="width: 50%; text-align: right; vertical-align: top;">
                              <span style="display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px; background-color: #E0F2FE; border: 1px solid #BAE6FD; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 11.5px; font-weight: 600; color: #075985; letter-spacing: 0.3px;">{{ statusLabel }}</span>
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                        </table>

                        <div style="height: 1px; background-color: #E8E3DC; margin-bottom: 16px;"></div>

                        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                          <tr>
                            <td style="width: 50%; padding-bottom: 14px; vertical-align: top;">
                              <p style="margin: 0 0 3px; font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9CA3AF;">Catégorie</p>
                              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: #1C1917;">{{ category }}</p>
                            </td>
                            <td style="width: 50%; padding-bottom: 14px; vertical-align: top;">
                              <p style="margin: 0 0 3px; font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9CA3AF;">Localisation</p>
                              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: #1C1917;">{{ location }}</p>
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                          <tr>
                            <td colspan="2" style="vertical-align: top;">
                              <p style="margin: 0 0 3px; font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9CA3AF;">Titre</p>
                              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: #1C1917;">{{ title }}</p>
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                        </table>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                  <!-- CTA -->
                  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                    <a
                      href="{{ ticketUrl }}"
                      style="display: inline-block; padding: 15px 40px; background-color: #1C1917; color: #FDFCFB; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.5px;"
                    >
                      Ouvrir le ticket →
                    </a>
                  </div>

                  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <a href="{{ platformUrl }}" style="font-size: 13px; color: #78716C; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: 300;">
                      Accéder à la plateforme
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 32px 20px 0;">
                <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="border-top: 1px solid #D6D3CD; padding-top: 24px; text-align: center;">
                      <p style="margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 12.5px; color: #A8A29E; font-weight: 300;">
                        Cet e-mail a été généré automatiquement par la plateforme {{ brandName }}.
                      </p>
                      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #C4BFB8; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.2px;">
                        © {{ new Date().getFullYear() }} {{ brandName }} · Tous droits réservés
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
